        <h2>Discover Kottayam</h2>
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/50/Kumarkom.jpg" alt="Vembanad Lake in Kottayam" width="800" height="400"> <p>Kottayam, nestled in the heart of Kerala, India, is a picturesque town known for its rich cultural heritage, lush landscapes, and serene backwaters. Often referred to as "Akshara Nagari" (City of Letters), it boasts a high literacy rate and a vibrant educational scene.</p>
        <p>Explore the tranquil Vembanad Lake, visit ancient churches and temples, and savor the delectable Kerala cuisine. Kottayam offers a unique blend of tradition and modernity, making it a must-visit destination.</p>
        <p>Learn more about Kottayam on <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kottayam" target="_blank">Wikipedia</a>.</p>
    </div>

